Make sure you have the following installed:

postgresql-8.1
libclass-dbi-pg-perl
perl
php4
libapache-mod-php4
libfreetype6
libpq3
php4-common
php4-gd
php4-pgsql
apache

If you are installing the logging package as a single sensor setup (without
the tunnel package) also install the following:

rrdtool
librrds-perl
clamav

After these packages are installed, start the installation of the logging package 
by running install_log.pl.
